LONG AND UNCOMFORTABLE LOOK AT

11:21.548 --> 11:22.315
WHETHER THE SPORT OUR THREE KIDS

11:22.315 --> 11:23.750
LOVE IS SAFE.

11:23.750 --> 11:24.851
THE BENEFITS THEY GET OUT OF THE

11:24.851 --> 11:26.119
GAME?

