12:18.504 --> 12:19.839
IDEA WAS DRIVEN HOME BY AN AWFUL

12:19.839 --> 12:21.608
TRAGEDY IN OUR TOWN.

12:21.608 --> 12:23.576
A 16 YEAR-OLD FOOTBALL PLAYER AT

12:23.576 --> 12:25.111
MONTCLAIR HIGH SCHOOL, RYNE

