DOUGHERTY, DIED FROM A BRAIN

12:26.012 --> 12:27.313
HEMORRHAGE HE GOT TACKLING

12:27.313 --> 12:28.848
DURING A GAME.

12:28.848 --> 12:29.749
THREE WEEKS BEFORE, HE'D HAD

12:29.749 --> 12:30.783
ANOTHER HARD HIT AND A

12:30.783 --> 12:32.518
CONCUSSION.

12:32.518 --> 12:33.519
THE WHOLE TOWN WAS REALLY SHAKEN

12:33.519 --> 12:34.887
UP BY HIS DEATH.

12:34.887 --> 12:35.989
DID WE CONSOLE OURSELVES,

12:35.989 --> 12:37.256
THINKING, WELL, THAT COULDN'T

