MAYBE.

12:42.195 --> 12:42.929
BUT WE KEPT SIGNING THE KIDS UP,

12:42.929 --> 12:43.963
AND THEY WERE PLAYING AND LOVING

12:43.963 --> 12:48.034
SOCCER.

12:48.034 --> 12:49.636
>> I REALLY LIKE PLAYING, HOW

12:49.636 --> 12:50.837
THERE ARE POSITIONS, BECAUSE

12:50.837 --> 12:52.271
THERE'S, LIKE, A SPECIAL THING

12:52.271 --> 12:53.706
THAT YOU HAVE TO DO WHEN YOU'RE

12:53.706 --> 12:55.174
DOING IT SO YOU FEEL LIKE YOU'RE

12:55.174 --> 12:56.676
AN IMPORTANT PART OF IT.

12:56.676 --> 13:00.413
>> YOU GET TO MOVE AROUND A LOT,

13:00.413 --> 13:03.349
AND THAT YOU HAVE TO BE A GOOD

13:03.349 --> 13:04.717
TEAM, NOT JUST BE COMPOSED OF

13:04.717 --> 13:05.385
GOOD PLAYERS.

