>> Reporter: THAT SAID, I CAN'T

13:08.588 --> 13:09.422
PRETEND THAT DR. FLYER'S

13:09.422 --> 13:10.356
WARNINGS WEREN'T ALWAYS

13:10.356 --> 13:11.257
SOMEWHERE IN THE BACK OF OUR

13:11.257 --> 13:13.993
MINDS.

