WITHIN THE LAST YEAR, AT LEAST

13:30.910 --> 13:32.278
THREE OF JACK'S TEAMMATES HAVE

13:32.278 --> 13:33.246
SUFFERED CONCUSSIONS.

13:33.246 --> 13:33.980
DID THAT MAKE US THINK ABOUT

13:33.980 --> 13:34.814
TAKING JACK OR ANY OF OUR KIDS

13:34.814 --> 13:35.815
OUT OF SOCCER?

13:35.815 --> 13:38.618
HONESTLY, NO.

13:38.618 --> 13:40.820
SEEING THEM LEARN THE VALUE OF

13:40.820 --> 13:41.988
HARD WORK AND DEDICATION, HOW TO

13:41.988 --> 13:43.589
HANDLE THE SUCCESSES AND THE

13:43.589 --> 13:44.724
FAILURES, IT ALL SEEMED WORTH IT

13:44.724 --> 13:45.925
TO US.

13:45.925 --> 13:47.960
>> IN THIS DAY AND AGE, THERE'S

13:47.960 --> 13:49.295
SO MANY WARNINGS, PARENTAL

13:49.295 --> 13:50.463
WARNINGS.

