>> AND IT GIVES THEM A LOT OF

14:17.557 --> 14:18.658
PLEASURE, SO I WASN'T PREPARED

14:18.658 --> 14:19.792
TO TAKE THAT AWAY FROM THEM.

14:19.792 --> 14:20.893
>> Reporter: BUT THEN, DURING

