OF THOSE REALLY BRUTAL BLOWS TO

14:25.998 --> 14:27.533
THE HEAD, I READ THIS STORY

14:27.533 --> 14:29.202
ABOUT A MOVEMENT TO TAKE HEADING

14:29.202 --> 14:30.636
OUT OF KID'S SOCCER BECAUSE OF

14:30.636 --> 14:33.206
CONCERN OVER CONCUSSIONS.

14:33.206 --> 14:34.373
I RAISED THIS QUESTION WITH A

14:34.373 --> 14:35.541
FRIEND WHO'S SPENT HIS ENTIRE

14:35.541 --> 14:36.909
LIFE AROUND THE GAME.

14:36.909 --> 14:37.610
DECLAN CARNEY WAS BORN IN

14:37.610 --> 14:39.312
IRELAND.

14:39.312 --> 14:40.513
HE MANAGES MY SON JACK'S TEAM,

14:40.513 --> 14:41.247
AND OUR SONS HAVE PLAYED

14:41.247 --> 14:42.882
TOGETHER FOR SEVERAL YEARS.

14:42.882 --> 14:44.417
>> THERE'S NO QUESTION THAT

14:44.417 --> 14:46.018
CONCUSSIONS NEED TO BE DEALT

14:46.018 --> 14:47.253
WITH AND NEED TO BE TAKEN VERY

14:47.253 --> 14:48.888
SERIOUSLY WHENEVER THEY HAPPEN.

14:48.888 --> 14:51.257
BUT IF SOCCER, HEADING A SOCCER

14:51.257 --> 14:52.892
BALL WAS ACTUALLY A REAL DANGER

14:52.892 --> 14:54.660
OF SOME SORT OF BRAIN INJURY, I

14:54.660 --> 14:56.429
THINK IT WOULD'VE EXHIBITED

