IT WOULD BE IN A LOW-RISK GROUP.

16:33.392 --> 16:35.595
>> Reporter: CANTU TOLD ME THAT

16:35.595 --> 16:38.097
HEADING THE BALL AS WELL AS THE

16:38.097 --> 16:40.233
COLLISIONS AND THE HARD FALLS TO

16:40.233 --> 16:41.367
THE GROUND THAT OFTEN ACCOMPANY

16:41.367 --> 16:42.368
THEM ARE PROBLEMATIC FOR KIDS

16:42.368 --> 16:44.503
BECAUSE UNLIKE ADULT BRAINS,

16:44.503 --> 16:45.438
KIDS' BRAINS ARE STILL

16:45.438 --> 16:46.172
DEVELOPING.

