IT HELPS TRANSMISSION, BUT IT

16:56.048 --> 16:58.517
ALSO GIVES STRENGTH.

16:58.517 --> 17:00.019
AND SO, WHEN YOU VIOLENTLY SHAKE

17:00.019 --> 17:01.721
THE YOUNG BRAIN, YOU HAVE A MUCH

17:01.721 --> 17:04.190
GREATER CHANCE TO DISRUPT NERVE

17:04.190 --> 17:05.892
FIBERS AND THEIR CONNECTIONS

17:05.892 --> 17:07.260
THAN YOU DO AN ADULT BRAIN.

