19:28.768 --> 19:29.835
ENOUGH TO PROTECT KIDS FROM HEAD

19:29.835 --> 19:32.038
INJURY.

19:32.038 --> 19:32.905
WE REACHED OUT TO FIFA AND TO

19:32.905 --> 19:33.839
THE U.S. SOCCER FEDERATION FOR

19:33.839 --> 19:35.207
COMMENT.

