WHILE NEITHER WOULD GO ON THE

19:36.542 --> 19:38.844
RECORD, CITING THE LITIGATION,

19:38.844 --> 19:39.612
THEY BOTH SAID THAT PLAYER

19:39.612 --> 19:41.981
SAFETY IS A PRIORITY, AND THE

19:41.981 --> 19:43.816
FEDERATION INDICATED HEADING AND

19:43.816 --> 19:45.251
CONCUSSIONS ARE AMONG THE TOPICS

19:45.251 --> 19:46.819
REGULARLY REVIEWED BY ITS POLICY

19:46.819 --> 19:49.255
MAKERS.

19:49.255 --> 19:50.389
BACK IN NEW JERSEY, THE SOCCER

19:50.389 --> 19:52.491
SEASON GOES ON.

