IT'S NOT SAFE FOR CHILDREN TO DO

20:48.914 --> 20:50.282
THIS.

20:50.282 --> 20:52.751
IT'S A CONTACT SPORT.

20:52.751 --> 20:54.120
YOU KNOW, THAT'S ALMOST A

20:54.120 --> 20:55.454
EUPHEMISM.

